      <title>匈牙利在通货膨胀加速后维持基准利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/hungary-keeps-key-interest-rate-steady-after-inflation-quickens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通货膨胀加速且匈牙利货币兑欧元汇率维持在两年低点附近后，匈牙利央行将其基准利率维持在欧盟最高水平之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/hungary-keeps-key-interest-rate-steady-after-inflation-quickens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 13:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩洛哥下调基准利率以刺激世界杯投资热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/morocco-cuts-key-rate-in-boost-for-world-cup-investment-spree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩洛哥今年第二次降息，降低借贷成本，以鼓励大规模投资活动，包括筹备共同举办 2030 年世界杯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/morocco-cuts-key-rate-in-boost-for-world-cup-investment-spree</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 12:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
